  "title": "CHEF",
  "description": "<p>Foodshop within neighbourhood vicinities requires chief cook for local food.</p><p>Permanently night shift.</p><p>Must be able to work on weekend and public holidays.</p><p>Must have good knowledge about food hygiene.</p><p>Must be willing to impart your cooking skills to your assistant.</p><p>Must be able to co-ordinate well with the counter-staffs.</p><p>Must know how to take inventory to ensure no shortage of ingredients at all times (however not to stock-pile especially those perishable items).</p><p>Must have at least three years of similar working experience.</p><p>Must be a team player.</p>",
